            <p>Have you installed ZendService\ReCaptcha? It must be installed in order for that captcha adapter to work.</p>

<p>The repository is here: <a href="https://github.com/zendframework/ZendService_ReCaptcha">https://github.com/zendframework/…</a></p>

<p>You can add it to composer using the package name "zendframework/zendservice-recaptcha", or via pyrus using the package name "zendservicerecaptcha". Alternately, grab a tarball/zipball from the git repository, unpack it, and add autoloader configuration that will pick it up.</p>

